description: Very Happy Mother’s Day to this special one. Thanks for keeping us all on the straight and narrow - we luv ya X x x
Very Happy Mother’s Day to this special one. Thanks for keeping us all on the straight and narrow - we luv ya X x x

My heart goes out to Dave and the band and Taylor’s beautiful family. This photo was always a cherished memory of a chance meeting on Carnaby Street - where the universe smiled on me and gave me a super chilled 10 minute chat with a legend that I idolized. This was the day before they headlined Reading Festival that year. Taylor was searching for a studio, being a total tourist on a few spare hours he had. My friend Lee and I spotted him being incognito in a bar and after striking up a convo, we directed him to another pub down the road where he was meeting some friends (and then proceeded to follow him around all evening!). Lovely memory, very lucky to have met him in such a natural way with time to just chat. Special guy and one of a kind. What a loss.
